        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="xmx8Y5nSZ1Oc5vyaJ7Zq-43" value="Currently I am working with a UK based customer and the use case for the customer is that they have turbine engines in place and if the turbine engine temperature is increased beyond a temperature, there is a huge breakdown in the system and a big loss for the customer." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="383.06" y="3080" width="452.94" height="60" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="xmx8Y5nSZ1Oc5vyaJ7Zq-44" value="For the same, Our team have developed a IOT based monitoring application and ingested the data in the system." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffe6cc;strokeColor=#d79b00;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="380.90999999999997" y="3140" width="452.94" height="40" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="xmx8Y5nSZ1Oc5vyaJ7Zq-45" value="So for this application, we have 6 developers, 2 frontend, 3 backend and 1 database engineer." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="380.36999999999995" y="3180" width="452.94" height="40" as="geometry" />
