        <mxCell id="S_FwkujRHl368Auy6BzO-143" value="&lt;b&gt;Tell me about Yourself&lt;/b&gt;" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#1ba1e2;strokeColor=#006EAF;fontColor=#ffffff;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1501.6699999999998" y="9710" width="640" height="30" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="S_FwkujRHl368Auy6BzO-144" value="I am xyz working in Axion Systems . I have total 10 years of experience from that from last 5 years I am working as a DevSecOps Consultant." style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffe6cc;strokeColor=#d79b00;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1501.6699999999998" y="9740" width="640" height="40" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="S_FwkujRHl368Auy6BzO-145" value="Currently, I am working in a &lt;b&gt;very interesting project &lt;/b&gt;where I am wokring as a devsecops consultant for a &lt;b&gt;big petroleum company&lt;/b&gt; where we are working on a monitroing and alerting dashboard app for petroleum refineries." style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1501.6699999999998" y="9780" width="640" height="30" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="S_FwkujRHl368Auy6BzO-146" value="The Applciations business use case is this customer have a lot of refineries across the globe and there are multiple motors/pumps in each of the refinery so there is a Industrial IOT device already created by the electrical Engineering team which is connected to the motor and it send RPM, temperature and other metrics to the Azure Event hub." style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffe6cc;strokeColor=#d79b00;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1501.6699999999998" y="9810" width="640" height="60" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="S_FwkujRHl368Auy6BzO-147" value="Using the data that we receive in event hub, Our Team is creating a Monitoring and Alerting Dashbaord Application which is a 3 tier application. For that we have a frontend backend and database... Our frontend is written in React, backend in Python and Database is PostgreSQL." style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1500.5599999999997" y="9870" width="640" height="60" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="S_FwkujRHl368Auy6BzO-148" value="For frontend, there are around 7-8 developers, For backend there are around 10-12 developers and database is also managed by the backend team." style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffe6cc;strokeColor=#d79b00;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1500.56" y="9930" width="640" height="30" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="S_FwkujRHl368Auy6BzO-149" value="My Responsibility in the Project is to Design the Landing zone, Automating Infra Deployment using Terraform and Creating and Maintaining CICD Pipelines in azure devops." style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1500.56" y="9960" width="640" height="50" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="vOCS-h0Zns1alFFI2X5f-1" value="If you allow, I can explain the Landing Zone, terraform code and the cicd pipelines that we have designed in the project?" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffe6cc;strokeColor=#d79b00;fontStyle=0" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1499.9999999999998" y="10010" width="640" height="30" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
