        <mxCell id="vOCS-h0Zns1alFFI2X5f-189" value="and inside dev folder we are calling the required modules for dev, and similarly for qa and prod folder we are calling the required modules for qa and prod environments.&lt;br&gt;In each environment folder we have set the backend block and we are storing our statefiles in azure storage accounts." style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffe6cc;strokeColor=#d79b00;fontStyle=0" parent="1" vertex="1">
