        <mxCell id="ys3-T1RIbLTgXLGHq-1d-69" value="4. Source Code Management ( GitHub, Azure Repo, BitBucket, GitLab)" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontStyle=1" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1710.36" y="11994.5" width="472.41" height="25" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ys3-T1RIbLTgXLGHq-1d-70" value="The technology to store the code with branching strategy is Git." style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffe6cc;strokeColor=#d79b00;fontStyle=1" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1725.36" y="12019.5" width="472.41" height="25" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ys3-T1RIbLTgXLGHq-1d-71" value="1. Protection policy enable hota hai (Direct koi main branch me push nahi kr skta hai)" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;fontStyle=0" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1725.36" y="12044.5" width="472.41" height="39" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ys3-T1RIbLTgXLGHq-1d-72" value="2. Hmesha push krne ke lie branching strategy hota hai" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;fontStyle=0" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1725.36" y="12083.5" width="472.41" height="30" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ys3-T1RIbLTgXLGHq-1d-73" value="3. Infra ke code ki branching Strategy ko bolenge trunk based branching strategy." style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;fontStyle=0" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1725.36" y="12113.5" width="472.41" height="30" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ys3-T1RIbLTgXLGHq-1d-74" value="4. jaise hi koi requirement aaya ek naya rg banana, we will clone main branch and will create feature branch from main branch" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;fontStyle=0" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1725.36" y="12143.5" width="472.41" height="40" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ys3-T1RIbLTgXLGHq-1d-75" value="5. We will push changes to feature branch" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;fontStyle=0" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1725.36" y="12183.5" width="472.41" height="30" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ys3-T1RIbLTgXLGHq-1d-76" value="6. Push krne ke lie git add ., git commit and git push krte hai.." style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;fontStyle=0" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1725.36" y="12213.5" width="472.41" height="30" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ys3-T1RIbLTgXLGHq-1d-77" value="7. Jaise hi changes feature branch me push hota hai remote repo p, automatic yaml pipeline based multistage pipeline chlne lgta hai" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;fontStyle=0" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1725.36" y="12243.5" width="472.41" height="40" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ys3-T1RIbLTgXLGHq-1d-78" value="8. Pehle stage me sara scanning hota hai (Trufflehog, Tflint, Tfsec, gitleaks, Terratest opencost, chef inspect etc..)" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;fontStyle=0" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1725.36" y="12283.5" width="472.41" height="40" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ys3-T1RIbLTgXLGHq-1d-79" value="&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;9. Second stage me plan hota hai jaha pr sb init, validate, fmt, connectivity to azure using azure connection and terraform plan&lt;/span&gt;" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;fontStyle=1" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1725.36" y="12323.5" width="472.41" height="40" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ys3-T1RIbLTgXLGHq-1d-80" value="&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;10. If both stages are good, We will raise Pull Request.&lt;/span&gt;" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;fontStyle=1" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1725.36" y="12363.5" width="472.41" height="30" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ys3-T1RIbLTgXLGHq-1d-81" value="&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;11. PR will be reviewed by GitHub Copilot AI and Team members (Lead/Architect)&lt;/span&gt;" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;fontStyle=1" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1725.36" y="12393.5" width="472.41" height="30" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ys3-T1RIbLTgXLGHq-1d-82" value="&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;12. As soon as its merged in the main branch, again a pipeline will run and that will run all the scan, plan stage and it will run apply also..&lt;/span&gt;" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;fontStyle=1" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1725.36" y="12423.5" width="472.41" height="30" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ys3-T1RIbLTgXLGHq-1d-83" value="4 Ghnta me se office me chatgpt phone me use karo mobile app" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffe6cc;strokeColor=#d79b00;fontStyle=0" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1725.36" y="12483.5" width="453.39" height="25" as="geometry" />
